      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2. Nominal inputs derived from manufacturer-supplied geometry and published blood rheology data; sensitivity to ±5% viscosity variation assessed informally and found negligible on NIH."
    },
