    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with medium model influence. PIV velocity field comparison and hemolysis index validation both demonstrate adequate predictive accuracy within acceptance thresholds. The prior-studies synthesis provides additional qualitative confidence in model form selection. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
